<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://andrian064.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/jenis-jenis-pipa-air-fungsinya.webp" alt="Jenis-Jenis Pipa Air" class="wp-image-2010" /></figure>
